                <p>Shoot us a note and we'd be glad to talk about your technology challenge free of charge. Many times we may not be the right fit, but we're glad to help you down the right path and find someone who is!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4 text-center">
                <i class="fa fa-envelope-o fa-3x wow bounceIn" data-wow-delay=".1s"></i>
                <p><a href="mailto:info@barnardtech.com">info@barnardtech.com</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
